OL,3,CTamworth forward refuses to play after
OL,4,Cclub reaction to racism
OL,6,FTamworth forward Chris Wreh says he
OL,7,Fmade himself unavailable for their
OL,8,Fmidweek game as he felt the club had
OL,9,Fnot supported him enough after he was
OL,10,Fracially abused.
OL,12,FWreh received abuse on social media
OL,13,Ffollowing Tamworth's FA Cup third-
OL,14,Fround defeat against Tottenham.
OL,16,FThe forward was brought on in the
OL,17,Fsecond half as the part-time National
OL,18,FLeague side took the Premier League
OL,19,Fside to extra time and lost 3-0.
