OL,6,FWreh posted on social media with a
OL,7,Fscreenshot showing the abuse that he
OL,8,Freceived on Tuesday 14 January, adding
OL,9,Fthat he would not play in that
OL,10,Fevening's fixture against Boldmere St
OL,11,FMichaels.
OL,13,FHe shared an update with his followers
OL,14,Fsaying that police are now
OL,15,Finvestigating the incident.
