OL,6,FWreh said: "I would like to extend my
OL,7,Fgratitude to the Tamworth supporters
OL,8,Fand members of the public who have
OL,9,Freached out to offer their support and
OL,10,Fassistance in identifying the
OL,11,Findividual responsible.
OL,13,F"Incidents like this highlight the
OL,14,Fongoing issue of racism. It is
OL,15,Fshameful to be racially abused by
OL,16,Fsomeone simply because they lost a
OL,17,Fbet, but sadly, this happens all too
OL,18,Foften".
