OL,6,F"Unfortunately, I will not be
OL,7,Favailable for this evening's game.
OL,8,FWhile I have the utmost respect for my
OL,9,Fmanager, who has supported me
OL,10,Fthroughout this issue, I am
OL,11,Fdisappointed that the club has not
OL,12,Fpublicly supported me yet, which has
OL,13,Fleft me feeling confused and
OL,14,Fdisappointed.
OL,16,F"Although we are well compensated to
OL,17,Fplay football and for many it is a
OL,18,Fdream job, we are also human beings.
