OL,3,CTamworth forward refuses to play after
OL,4,Cclub reaction to racism
OL,6,F"I have received only one call from an
OL,7,Fofficial at the club, more than 36
OL,8,Fhours after the incident. At no point
OL,9,Fwas I asked if I was okay, instead, I
OL,10,Fwas informed that the silence was due
OL,11,Fto a desire to keep the matter
OL,12,Finternal. I cannot agree with or
OL,13,Fcondone this approach."
OL,15,F"If these incidents are kept 'in-
OL,16,Fhouse', they will never be addressed.
OL,17,FI hope everyone understands my reasons
OL,18,Ffor speaking out."
