OL,6,FWreh, an American international,
OL,7,Fjoined Tamworth in 2023 and previously
OL,8,Fplayed for other Midlands sides
OL,9,FStratford Town and Rushall Olympic.
OL,11,FStaffordshire Police have said: "We're
OL,12,Faware of a social media message
OL,13,Finvolving racist abuse that was sent
OL,14,Fonline to a player following the FA
OL,15,FCup match between Tamworth and
OL,16,FTottenham Hotspur on Sunday 12
OL,17,FJanuary."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/8
