OL,6,F"Officers are continuing to liaise
OL,7,Fwith Tamworth Football Club and
OL,8,Fnational policing partners as part of
OL,9,Ftheir initial enquiries and plans to
OL,10,Fsupport the victim moving forward.
OL,11,FRacist abuse will never be tolerated
OL,12,Fand officers will thoroughly
OL,13,Finvestigate any reports as robustly as
OL,14,Fpossible to ensure those responsible
OL,15,Fare dealt with accordingly."
OL,17,FIn response, Tamworth FC have said it
OL,18,Fwill "continue to support Chris" and
OL,19,Fthat they "have and will always
OL,20,Fsupport it's players against any sign
OL,21,Fof racism and discrimination".
